Class HashSet<A>

java.lang.Object
  fj.data.HashSet<A>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<A>
public final class HashSet<A>
extends Object
implements Iterable<A>

A mutable hash set that guarantees uniqueness of its elements providing O(1) lookup.
